# Runtimes for the cloud-evidence collector (asdf / mise).
# The collector runs on Node (via tsx), Bun, AND Deno — see RUNBOOK "Runtime".
# Bun is recommended for production collection (native TS, faster startup/I/O,
# better concurrency under load). Node + tsx remains the default/fallback and is
# what the vitest test suite runs on. Deno works too (npm deps resolve from
# node_modules) but requires explicit --allow-* permission flags; see the
# `collect:deno` / `verify:deno` npm scripts.
nodejs 22.10.0
bun 1.3.14
deno 2.8.1
